data.description: Hard to find 1-story boasting 2,547 SF of living space which includes 364 SF sun room off family rm.  3 bedrms, 2 1/2 bathrms & 2-car garage.  Brick & vinyl home for easy exterior maintenance.  You are greeted with formal foyer.  Spacious living rm w/bay window & crown molding.  Formal dining rm w/crown molding.  Combined kitchen & breakfast rm has quartz counters, pull-out shelving, soft-close drawers, pantry, overhead lighting & breakfast bar.  Family rm  w/fp & hardwood flrs (not warranted)  French doors off family rm lead to sun rm w/cathedral ceilings & vinyl tilt-in windows.  6-panel doors in most of home.  Updated vinyl tilt-in windows through most of home.  Separate utility rm off breakfast rm.  All kitchen appliances included.  Garage has an 11x11 extra rm w/ac unit - ideal workshop or hobby rm.  Patio.  4/10 acre lot.  Convenient to shopping, dining, library, Archer Park, Kettering Health Network & schools. 1-year Home Warranty.  Bring your decorating ideas.  Easy to show.
